name: Charro de Jalisco
description:
This is my alter ego, folkloric dance represents me. Since I was a child I was restless and I was passionate about dance, hitting the ground with my feet and allowing myself to express myself with that. This is an image of me intervened with editing software in which I am being happy dancing on the other side of the world (Canton, China).
I felt very happy expressing myself from the body, the movement and the music, this image reflects all the emotions and sensations that I lived at that time with respect to my country, my land.
